descriptionHtml:
Here we go again Battleaxe for 2 hands ready.

--------------------------------------

Another update; The quiver and arrows are done!

---------------------------------------
So I started to do some more stuff for the Elven Weapons.
So far we have a Bow and a Sword 1H.
More to come hopefully!

Feel free to modify and comment!

---------------------
How to install:
Extract the zip file to the Skyrim\\Data folder.

Uninstall:

Simply delete these 3 files for the sword:
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\sword\\sword_d.dds
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\sword\\sword_m.dds 
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\sword\\sword_n.dds

Simply delete these 3 files for the bow:
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\bow\\bow.dds
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\bow\\bow_m.dds
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\bow\\bow_n.dds

Simply delete these 3 files for quiver:
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\arrow\\Quiver.dds
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\arrow\\Quiver_m.dds
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\arrow\\Quiver_n.dds

Simply delete these 3 files: for the battleaxe
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\Battleaxe\\elvenBattleaxe.dds
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\Battleaxe\\elvenBattleaxe_m.dds
Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\weapons\\elven\\Battleaxe\\elvenBattleaxe_n.dds

Nexus Mod Manager compatible!

Enjoy!

Contact: Spamheinz@web.de
